Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "title": "Task 01",
    "description": "Task 01",
    "expirationDate": "2024-01-01"
}

###
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/task/b4537ce0-be4e-480b-a900-43062a464783 HTTP/1.1
